node.text: Meet two of the talented creators who participated in our first ever global social media competition for the launch of our new Iconic Motion. Hear how they started with videography, built their following on TikTok and created their beautiful videos. #DanielWellington #IconicMotion

A #DWmoment from @Brittenelle, an influencer and creator based in Los Angeles, on life, destiny, and freedom.

What's your moment?
Share your moment by using the #DWmoments.
http://bit.ly/momentDW 
#DanielWellington

node.title: "The moment I left it all behind" #DWmoments by @brittenelle

To celebrate the year he turns 30 and 10 years since he first started his journey to become one of the world's biggest superstars, @LayZhang is releasing another exclusive collaboration with Daniel Wellington. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀

DW X LAY ZHANG. For the third year in a row, we are thrilled to introduce an exclusive limited-edition timepiece created with international superstar @layzhang. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Since his debut 10 years ago, Lay has found himself reflecting on each step that has made up his successful career today. This reflection has allowed him to continue moving forward to pursue his ambitions and create the future that he envisioned since the beginning. This DW X Lay Limited edition timepiece captures the philosophy behind each of Lay’s achievements - to make every step count.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
